text: Guillermo Díaz Gea (born 16 February 1944) is a Mexican politician from the Institutional Revolutionary Party. He has served as Deputy of the LV and LVIII Legislatures of the Mexican Congress representing Veracruz. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Veracruz Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Institutional Revolutionary Party politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
